  "keyFeatures": [
    "Resident-Town-Nation hierarchy with grid-based land claim protection",
    "Economy integration via Vault for town/nation banks, taxes, and upkeep",
    "Granular permission system with townyperms.yml and LuckPerms/Vault support",
    "Multiple plot types: Residential, Shop, Embassy, Arena, Farm, Inn, Jail, Wilds, Bank",
    "FlatFile and MySQL/SQLite database backends",
    "Developer API (TownyAPI) with events, metadata, and command addon system",
    "Folia and Paper support",
    "PlaceholderAPI integration",
    "Outpost system, jailing, and outlaw management",
    "Nation zones, allies, enemies, and diplomacy"
  ],
